For Challenges with Zotero| Not connecting to word document!

The way out is to start with search %Appdata% this way on start icon of the computer.
After this copy the document that you have just downloaded front the zotoro website https://www.zotero.org/support/word_processor_plugin_manual_installation
copy the dot.m document and push them to this path C:\Users\::username::\AppData\Roaming\Microsoft\Word\STARTUP
Delete the one there and put in another one.

/* I must not run into this kind of problem again */
